<item>
            <title>[LU-8871] kernel upgrade [SLES12 SP2 4.4.21-84]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8871</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SLES12 SP2 recently became public.  It is now freely downloadable from suse.com.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This mod represents a major shift in the supported linux version in SLES12.  While all previous SLES12 releases were based on linux 3.12, SLES12 SP2 is based on linux 4.4.  Among other things this means that very different patches are needed for ldiskfs and server support.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
